cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.ET

The paper deals with layout pattern sampling and hotspot detection, which are related to computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes an active learning-based approach, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (AI) and data mining (DM), making cs.AI and cs.DM likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the paper deals with VLSI design, which is related to computer architecture (CA) and embedded systems (ET), making cs.ET a possible sub-category.
